summary: An ordinance discontinuing the eminent domain proceedings to acquire land and other property in Blocks 26 and 35, Mercer's 2nd Addition to North Seattle, and portions of vacated streets adjoining, as contemplated by Ordinance No. 86049, King County Cause No. 507551; providing for the repeal of said ordinance and for the payment of the taxable costs.
committee: Finance and Parks and Public Grounds
